    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款3D版‘杀戮尖塔’类策略卡牌闯关游戏，游戏画面精致细腻，氛围感十足，远超同类型游戏。游戏玩法在保留卡牌游戏的精髓下舍弃了复杂的无用功能和系统，且简单易上手，无需玩家费时学习，研究，与攻略，搭配合适自己的卡牌即可一战爽到底，就这么简单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094560/extras/c52ee52f00d71caaaa0ab1e00ee1c2d9.avif?t=1750455225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094560/extras_big/c52ee52f00d71caaaa0ab1e00ee1c2d9.avif?t=1750455225 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过以下操作将游戏语言设置为中文：点击游戏菜单中的“Settings”选项，在设置窗口中将“XXX”从“EN”改为“ZN”，然后返回即可。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态构建的牌组：选择你的卡牌！在挑战的途中解锁近百张不同的卡牌，选择是否将它们加入你的牌组，通过组合搭配让卡牌组发挥意想不到的效果，打败敌人、挑战到底。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094560/extras/fb7d1eabe873234550d71ac94d00bb5b.avif?t=1750455225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094560/extras_big/fb7d1eabe873234550d71ac94d00bb5b.avif?t=1750455225 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同选择的地图：每次开始挑战时，地图的路线都提供了不同选择。是选择高风险高回报，还是谨慎前行？面对不同的敌人、选择不同的卡牌、发现不同的装备、以及随机事件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094560/extras/c3c466cb7063c627197ee886db667e2c.avif?t=1750455225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094560/extras_big/c3c466cb7063c627197ee886db667e2c.avif?t=1750455225 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >威力强大的装备：在地图中你将发现各种黑科技装备，这些装备会与你的牌组产生强大的化学反应，让你的战力得到飞跃。但也不要过于强求，这样也许会让你付出更多代价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094560/extras/b7b7c5001a83d0a21071959255fbcb7c.avif?t=1750455225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094560/extras_big/b7b7c5001a83d0a21071959255fbcb7c.avif?t=1750455225 width=800 height=430 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《OMEGA卡牌冒险》已完成先行版本，目前游戏共有以下内容：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6名角色，各自拥有独特的属性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100张左右可用的卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10多种可被找到的功能性装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50多场完全不同的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10件左右神秘的事件，能给你带来帮助，也能给你造成伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
